**Privacy Policy**

**Effective Date:** March 5th 2025

**1. Introduction**
Welcome to linkedin analyzer ("we," "our," or "us"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data when you use our application.

**2. Information We Collect**
We collect the following data from LinkedIn when users authorize our app:

- Name
- LinkedIn profile data (e.g., job title, location, profile picture)
- Posts and content shared publicly on LinkedIn

**3. How We Use Your Information**
We use this data to:

- Provide insights for recruiters
- Analyze sentiment and professionalism in posts
- Improve our services

**4. Data Retention & Deletion**
We retain collected data only as long as necessary for our service. Users can request data deletion by contacting us at yonatan.assayag@gmail.com.

**5. Sharing of Data**
We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal data. Data may be shared only if required by law or with trusted service providers assisting in our operations.

**6. Security Measures**
We implement security practices to protect your data but cannot guarantee absolute security.

**7. Third-Party Services**
Our app may interact with third-party services such as LinkedIn. Please review their privacy policies to understand how they handle your data.

**8. Changes to This Privacy Policy**
We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.

**9. Contact Us**
For questions or data deletion requests, contact us at yonatan.assayag@gmail.com.

